headline.print_headline: 2004 US Open Champ Kuznetsova Loses in 1st Round
headline.main: 2004 US Open Champ Kuznetsova Loses in 1st Round

lead_paragraph: Svetlana Kuznetsova lost her first-round match at the U.S. Open for the first time since 2005, the year she was the tournament's defending champion.
